{
  "stem": "1292.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you want--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I just must go back to that and mention what a wonderful person my mother was and I said, she was most hospitable person.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we haven't been very wealthy and, you know, it wasn't everything of plenty like it is today.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my mother always did when-- whoever popped in-- and it wasn't by appointments like very often in Australia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just very spontaneous, and family and friend just popped in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother never, never did make feel anybody that didn't receive them empty-handed, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She always did have things to offer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember very often-- and I was angry about it at time-- my mother would happily give so many dinners, which was for her, she would happily give away to the cousin or whoever came in unexpected.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes it was-- and even after the Depression, you know, you only cook for a certain amount of people and but so she didn't mind at all.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was always happy to give whatever she has.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was wonderful person, I must say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, especially with my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, as I said, when the first soldiers arrive in-- German soldiers arrived in tanks and looking with their helmets and were so powerful and it was so-- do I-- should I repeat myself and say they did look indeed like from another planet, you know?",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was completely unknown to us technology and motoring and the uniforming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a very scary feeling, very scary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right from the start they was taking people, specially they spotted easily all those Orthodox people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took them to work to sweep the streets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They was offensive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would take them by the beards and, you know, shake them",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
